snitch
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a dislike or grudge (esp. in phrase to have/get a snitch on (someone))
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:cf. snitcher
